info.description:
PiPan        
        
        Overview
        --------
                
        PiPan for PiPan servo controller and PiLight. This package contains functions to control PiPan servo controller and PiLight from mindsensors.com.
                
        Products that use this library can be found at http://www.mindsensors.com/search?controller=search&orderby=position&orderway=desc&search_query=pi-pan&submit_search=.

        Documentation can be found at http://openelectrons.com/OEPiReference/html/
info.keywords: mindsensors, PiPan, PiLight, PiCam, servo, light
